    "customization_form_disclaimer": "<p data-block-key=\"ogxcs\"><b>Disclaimer</b></p><p data-block-key=\"qt8gf\">The following features and functionality are not available to teachers and students using Google Docs customized content:</p><ul><li data-block-key=\"5zbxh\"><b>Errata updates</b>. OpenStax webview is updated at least twice yearly. Customized Google Docs will not receive these content updates.</li><li data-block-key=\"rxpcx\"><b>Access to study tools</b>. OpenStax webview has in-book search, highlighting, study guides, and more available for free. This functionality will not be available in Google Docs versions.</li><li data-block-key=\"qf4nd\"><b>Formatting.</b> Print books and webview have a specific design and structure format developed for those platforms. These functionalities are not available in the Google Docs versions.</li></ul>",
